manic right now?

00:53:28.032 --> 00:53:29.740
Maybe I need to take
a couple steps back.

00:53:29.740 --> 00:53:30.640
Or is it--

00:53:30.640 --> 00:53:31.431
PAUL ENGLISH: Yeah.

