brick sort of lights up

00:53:57.100 --> 00:53:59.530
and it turns a different color.

00:53:59.530 --> 00:54:05.320
And I just become really, really
perceptive of things around me.

00:54:05.320 --> 00:54:07.050
And if there are
people in my car,

00:54:07.050 --> 00:54:09.740
