thing in the morning,

00:54:49.280 --> 00:54:53.380
I do know that I should
check with my psychiatrist,

00:54:53.380 --> 00:54:55.390
and just say, if
I've been going days

00:54:55.390 --> 00:54:57.284
at a time with very,
very little sleep,

00:54:57.284 --> 00:54:58.700
I should probably
have a med check

00:54:58.700 --> 00:55:00.830
and see if I need to do
something different just

00:55:00.830 --> 00:55:02.450
to keep me from
going a little bit

00:55:02.450 --> 00:55:04.840
too far where I
disconnect from reality,

00:55:04.840 --> 00:55:08.350
I disconnect from people, and I
make really rash decisions that

00:55:08.350 --> 00:55:09.554
